'''提拉·特基拉'''（{{lang-en|Tila Tequila}}，{{bd|1981年|10月24日}}），原名'''提拉·阮'''（{{lang-en|Tila Nguyen}}）、越南語名'''阮氏天青'''（{{lang-vi|Nguyễn Thị Thiên Thanh}}），是一位在[[新加坡|新加坡]]出生的[[越裔美國人|越裔美國]]女模特兒、電視人物、歌手、詞曲作家、演員、作家和網路部落客，家人於[[越南战争|越南战争]]结束后移居美国。

==爭議==
===親納粹言論===
在2013年12月，阮氏在其網站發表一份名為「我為什麼同情[[阿道夫·希特拉|希特拉]]：第一節」({{lang-en|Why I Sympathize with Hitler: Part I}})的文章，並且在其[[Facebook|Facebook]]專頁發表親希特拉和[[反猶太主義|反猶太]]言論。<ref name="tablet">{{cite news |author1=里爾·利波韋斯 (Liel Liebovitz) |title=Tila Tequila, Jew (?), Converts to Sexy Hitler |trans-title=猶太人(?)提拉·特基拉變身成為性感的納粹份子 |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work={{Link-en|石板雜誌|Tablet (magazine)}} |url=https://www.tabletmag.com/sections/news/articles/tila-tequila-jew-converts-to-sexy-hitler |date=2013-12-09 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301204144/https://www.tabletmag.com/sections/news/articles/tila-tequila-jew-converts-to-sexy-hitler |dead-url=no }}</ref>阮氏還公開了一張背景含有[[奧斯威辛集中營|奧斯威辛集中營]]前門的照片。照片中，一個衣著露骨的阮氏手握[[手槍|手槍]]，並且配戴了印上[[卍#近現代的意義|納粹卍標誌]]的臂章。<ref name="toi">{{cite news |title=UK reality show boots glamour model over Hitler support |trans-title=模特兒支持希特拉而被轟出英國真人實境節目 |url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/uk-reality-show-boots-glamor-model-over-support-for-hitler/ |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work=[[以色列時報|以色列時報]] |date=2015-08-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506212634/https://www.timesofisrael.com/uk-reality-show-boots-glamor-model-over-support-for-hitler/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Huffington Post">{{cite news |author1=亞伯拉罕·H·福克斯曼 (Abraham H. Foxman) |title=Anti-Semitism: The Week in Review |trans-title=反猶太主義：一周回顧 |url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/anti-semitism-the-week-in_b_4441621 |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work=[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]] |date=2014-02-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211105025745/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/anti-semitism-the-week-in_b_4441621 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

阮氏這些行為引起了其Facebook[[愛好者|擁躉]]的憤怒。Facebook當局後來移除了這些具爭議性的發文和照片，並且把她的戶口封禁。<ref name="Huffington Post"/>一年後，阮氏參加了英國電視節目[[名人老大哥_(電視節目)|名人老大哥]]第16季的拍攝，但當製作單位發現她曾經發表過的言論後便被勒令推出。<ref name="toi"/><ref>{{cite news |title=Tila Tequila thrown out of Celebrity Big Brother |trans-title=提拉·特基拉被轟出「名牌老大哥」 |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-34093252 |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work=[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]] |date=2015-08-28 |language=en |archive-date=2021-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211006093301/https://www.bbc.com/news/newsbeat-34093252 |dead-url=no }}</ref>阮氏隨後道歉，並說她發表那些言論時正受到[[物質依賴|毒癮]]和[[抑鬱症|抑鬱症]]的困擾。<ref>{{cite news |title=Tila Tequila apologizes for antisemitic comments after Big Brother exit |trans-title=提拉·特基拉退出「名人老大哥」後為她的反猶太言論道歉 |url=https://www.torontosun.com/2015/08/29/tila-tequila-apologizes-for-anti-semitic-comments-after-big-brother-exit |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work={{link-en|多倫多太陽報|Toronto Sun}} |date=2015-08-29 |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104215505/https://torontosun.com/2015/08/29/tila-tequila-apologizes-for-anti-semitic-comments-after-big-brother-exit |dead-url=no }}</ref>
在2016年，阮氏在[[Twitter|Twitter]]發表被認為是反猶太或親納粹的言論。當年4月，阮氏在希特拉的出生日向他祝賀，並且說她是希特拉轉世。<ref>{{cite news |author1=梅拉妮·多斯提斯 (Melanie Dostis) |title=Tila Tequila wishes Hitler happy birthday in shocking Twitter rant |trans-title=提拉·特基拉在Twitter發飆並祝賀希特拉生日快樂 |url=https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/tila-tequila-wishes-hitler-happy-birthday-shocking-twitter-ran-article-1.2609249 |accessdate=2021-05-02 |work=[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]] |date=2016-04-20 |language=en |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506081350/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/tila-tequila-wishes-hitler-happy-birthday-shocking-twitter-ran-article-1.2609249 |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年五月，阮氏在Twitter發文，說她的「議會」認為美國右翼政治評論員[[班·夏皮羅|班·夏皮羅]]應該被「噴毒氣，然後送返以色列」。<ref name="wearyourvoice">{{cite news |author1=安特萬·赫倫 (Antwan Herron) |title=Tila tequila is the racist celeb who thinks they’re relevant but never really was |trans-title=提拉·特基拉是一位認為自己是有影響力的種族歧視者名人，但她從來未真正有過影響力 |url=https://www.wearyourvoicemag.com/tila-tequila-racist-celeb-thinks-theyre-relevant-never-really/ |accessdate=2021-05-03 |work=Wear Your Voice雜誌 |date=2016-06-07 |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104213226/https://www.wearyourvoicemag.com/tila-tequila-racist-celeb-thinks-theyre-relevant-never-really/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>儘管阮氏是在新加坡出世的越裔人士，她在Facebook發文表示「這世上我只會為兩件事欣然犧牲我的性命：殺掉所有猶太人和保全白人種族。」<ref name="wearyourvoice"/>

在2016年11月19日，阮氏出席[[白人優越主義|白人至上主義]]團體{{link-en|國家政策研究院|National Policy Institute}}為慶祝[[當勞·特朗普|當勞·特朗普]][[2016年美國總統選舉|當選美國總統]]而舉辦的會議，並且在Twitter發布一張展示她使用[[納粹禮|納粹禮]]的照片，並觀上「勝利萬歲！」（Sieg heil!）和舉手狀[[表情圖標|表情圖標]]的推文。<ref>{{cite news |author1=凱特琳·嬈力 (Caitlin Yilek) |title='Alt-right' supporters celebrate Trump victory in D.C. |trans-title=「另類右派」支持者在首都華盛頓慶祝特朗普在總統選舉中勝出 |url=https://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/306915-alt-right-celebrates-trump-victory |accessdate=2021-05-05 |work=[[國會山報|國會山報]] |date=2016-11-19 |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104213216/https://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/306915-alt-right-celebrates-trump-victory |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/AngelTilaLove/status/799809348755161088|title=Seig heil! ("✋")|trans-title=勝利萬歲！("✋")|date=2016-11-19|access-date=2020-05-05|website=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131028/https://twitter.com/AngelTilaLove/status/799809348755161088|archive-date=2020-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref> 發文後，阮氏在Twitter的戶口被封禁，<ref>{{cite web|author1=艾蜜莉·海爾 (Emily Heil)|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2016/11/22/tila-tequilas-twitter-account-suspended-after-appearance-at-white-nationalist-convention/|title=Tila Tequila's Twitter account suspended after appearance at white nationalist convention|trans-title=提拉·特基拉的Twitter戶口在其出席白人民族主義團體團體會議後被封禁|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=November 22, 2016|access-date=November 22, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161123003252/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2016/11/22/tila-tequilas-twitter-account-suspended-after-appearance-at-white-nationalist-convention/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而阮氏隨後則加入了具爭議性的右翼社交網站[[Gab|Gab]]。<ref>{{cite news |author1=阿比·奧海薩 (Abby Ohlheiser) |title=Banned from Twitter? This site promises you can say whatever you want |trans-title=被Twitter封禁嗎？這個網站承諾你可以暢所欲言 |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/business/blue-sky/ct-twitter-ban-gab-wp-bsi-20161203-story.html |accessdate=2021-05-05 |work=[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]] ([[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]轉載) |date=2016-12-03 |archive-date=2021-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210718214330/https://www.chicagotribune.com/business/blue-sky/ct-twitter-ban-gab-wp-bsi-20161203-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

